clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: Estradiol dienanthate is not currently available in any FDA or Health Canada approved products

contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Estradiol the principal intracellular human estrogen is substantially more active than its metabolites estrone and estriol at the cellular level
